<h1 class="slogan">Enjoy your travels while "Living Like a Local"</h1>


<center>
<div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
  <ol class="carousel-indicators">
    <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
    <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
    <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
  </ol>
  <div class="carousel-inner">
    <div class="carousel-item active">
      <img class="photo" src="https://bit.ly/2CBEuec" height="500px" width="800px" class="d-block w-100">
      <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
       <h5 class="country">Thailand</h5>
        <p class="desc">This place is the true meaning of paradise.  Beautiful beaches, landscapes, and people, this beautiful 
        country is truly magical.  Experience the rumbling streets of Bangkok or escape to the peaceful mountains of Chiang
        Mai. Come get lost in the land of smiles.</p>
    </div>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <img class="photo" src="https://bit.ly/2RHQRjc" height="500px" width="800px" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
      <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
       <h5 class="country">Italy</h5>
        <p class="desc">Italy is a country people always return to.  From the north to the south this place has it all.  History, 
        beautiful beaches, cities made of waterways, and arguably the best food in the world.</p>
    </div>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <img class="photo" src="https://on.natgeo.com/2Fwz7ki" height="500px" width="800px" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
      <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
       <h5 class="country">Peru</h5>
        <p class="desc">Consistently on top of the world's best travel destinations Peru is a country like no other.
        One can indulge on the incredible food Peru has to offer and explore to the amazing Machiu Pichu, making 
        this a trip to remember.</p>
    </div>
    </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
      <img class="photo" src="https://bit.ly/2Hzhan0" height="500px" width="800px" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
      <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
       <h5 class="country">Austria</h5>
        <p class="desc">For those of you who enjoy a nice winter get away to a winter wonderland, Austria is the place for you.
        With some of the best ski slopes in the world skiiers and snowboarders will never want to leave.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
      <img class="photo" src="https://cdn.escapism.to/gallery/5b4a68d402b96.jpeg" height="500px" width="800px" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
      <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
       <h5 class="country">Cuba</h5>
        <p class="desc">Newly opened to American tourists Cuba is full of beautiful culture and vibrant colors.  
        Feel as if you've travelled back in time and enjoy the beauty of Cuba.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
  </a>
  <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
  </a>
</div>
</center>



